@startuml
title Notification Flow (AWS SNS + SQS with Retries, IAM, and KMS)

actor "API Client" as Client
participant "FastAPI Service" as API
participant "AwsSNSService" as SNS
participant "IAM Role/User" as IAM
participant "SQS Queue (KMS)" as SQS
participant "SQS DLQ (KMS)" as DLQ
participant "PyQt6 Desktop App" as Desktop

Client -> API: POST /notifications\n(subject, message)

API -> API: validateRequest()

API -> IAM: signed AWS request\n(temporary or user credentials)
API -> SNS: publish(subject, message)\n(retries on transient errors)

SNS -> SQS: sendMessage(payload)

loop Poll every 1s
    Desktop -> SQS: pollMessages()
    SQS --> Desktop: message(subject, message)
    Desktop -> Desktop: displayNotification()
end

SQS --> DLQ: redrive on maxReceiveCount

@enduml
